vote.title: Authorize (1) a one-year contract with two one-year renewal options for Mobile Community Healthcare Program services, with the University of Texas Southwestern Medical Center related to Network Access Improvement Program Medicaid patients, to be provided by the Dallas Fire-Rescue Department for the period July 1, 2020 through June 30, 2021; and (2) the receipt and deposit of revenue funds - Estimated Annual Revenue:  $180,000.00
